description: Non material amendment to planning permission ref: P/2013/5757 dated 07/03/2014 for change of use from office (Use Class B1) to a consulate facility (Sui-Generis Use); external alterations to building envelope including re-cladding and alterations to fenestration; alterations to parking layout, pedestrian access, landscaping and boundary treatment, refuse and recycling storage and bicycle storage (revisions to the design and extent of the perforated metal screen, omission of 1 no. proposed window to main building, replacement of existing door to the main building)
